Installation Instructions
=========================

Prerequisites:

    - tuyapp C++ library (installed and discoverable by the linker)
    - C99 compiler (gcc, clang)
    - C++ compiler (for linking)
    - GNU autotools (autoconf >= 2.69, automake, libtool)

Quick install:

    autoreconf -fi
    ./configure
    make
    make check
    sudo make install

The library installs to $prefix/lib and headers to $prefix/include/seatuya.

To specify an install prefix:

    ./configure --prefix=/usr/local

To uninstall:

    sudo make uninstall
